<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17590117-36">
               <interp inst="t17590117-36" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17590117-36" type="year" value="1759"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17590117-36" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17590117"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17590117-36" type="date" value="17590117"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17590117-36-off227-c332" targOrder="Y" targets="t17590117-36-defend405 t17590117-36-off227 t17590117-36-verdict230"></join>
         
               <p>104. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17590117-36-defend405" type="defendantName">
                     Celia 
                     Scott 
                  <interp inst="t17590117-36-defend405" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-defend405" type="given" value="Celia"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-defend405" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17590117-36-deflabel226" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17590117-36-defend405 t17590117-36-deflabel226"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17590117-36-off227" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-off227" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-off227" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one pewter chamber-pot, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17590117-36-victim407" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Girdler 
                  <interp inst="t17590117-36-victim407" type="surname" value="Girdler"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-victim407" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-victim407" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17590117-36-off227 t17590117-36-victim407"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17590117-36-cd228" type="crimeDate">Jan. 8</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17590117-36-off227 t17590117-36-cd228"></join>. ++</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17590117-36-person408">
                  Martha 
                  Girdler 
               <interp inst="t17590117-36-person408" type="surname" value="Girdler"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-person408" type="given" value="Martha"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-person408" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am wife to 
               <persName id="t17590117-36-person409">
                  John 
                  Girdler 
               <interp inst="t17590117-36-person409" type="surname" value="Girdler"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-person409" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-person409" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , we live <placeName id="t17590117-36-crimeloc229">near the Seven Dials</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17590117-36-crimeloc229" type="placeName" value="near the Seven Dials"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17590117-36-crimeloc229" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17590117-36-off227 t17590117-36-crimeloc229"></join>; I missed a pewter-chamber-pot from off the stairs; the prisoner worked for a lodger of mine, and had come down the stairs a little before we missed it; we took her up and charged her with taking it; she confessed she had taken it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17590117-36-person410">
                  Thomas 
                  Woodard 
               <interp inst="t17590117-36-person410" type="surname" value="Woodard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-person410" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-person410" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am constable: I had the prisoner in charge; she confessed she had stole the chamber-pot, and took me to her lodgings in Holbourn, where the pot was in a closet.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence.</p>
               <p>I worked in the prosecutrix's house with a lodger there; I was coming down stairs and wanted to carry a little water home, so took that pot; but did design to bring it again.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17590117-36-verdict230" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-verdict230" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17590117-36-punish231" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17590117-36-punish231" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17590117-36-defend405 t17590117-36-punish231"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
